第三集-小心负向思考

https://fenxiao.xiaoe-tech.com/#/try_page/1/app6b31gtp17812/v_5cb87f79bc0f3_XmVZhzLY

<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgb(192, 0, 0); font-size: 24px;"></span></p><p style="margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 27.2px; widows: 1; text-align: center;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(90, 90, 90);"><strong style="max-width: 100%;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: Arial; font-size: 17px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(192, 0, 0);">课程亮点</span></strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 27.2px; widows: 1; text-align: center;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(90, 90, 90);"><strong style="max-width: 100%;">《易经》是我们中华文化的源头，</strong><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; widows: 1; text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(90, 90, 90);"><strong style="max-width: 100%;">是天底下最明朗的一本书，</strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; widows: 1; text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(90, 90, 90);"><strong style="max-width: 100%;">直贯天人之际，</strong><strong style="max-width: 100%;">打通内圣外王，</strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; widows: 1; text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(90, 90, 90);"><strong style="max-width: 100%;">就凭一个真实中道。</strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; widows: 1; text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(90, 90, 90);"><strong style="max-width: 100%;">▼</strong></span></p><p><br/></p><section style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 27.2px; widows: 1;"><section style="max-width: 100%; background-image: url(&quot;http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/app6ovCb8Zj3569/image/ueditor/41957400_1555594795.cn/mmbiz_jpg/trcftmucdr9twf3m95yujpeiwe5jiit1vs1z8sl5h4fgoiclamib5ico3j43q4vr0heqydklic9ousfkykro15glga/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot;); background-size: 200px 200px; background-repeat: repeat;"><section style="padding: 15px; max-width: 100%;"><section style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.8em;"><p style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: center;"><strong style="max-width: 100%;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(123, 12, 0);">王镇华《易经的中道》</span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 8px; margin-left: 8px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><strong style="max-width: 100%;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(123, 12, 0);">• 用大白话，把中国文化的源头《易经》讲清楚。</span></strong></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px 10px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><strong style="max-width: 100%;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(123, 12, 0);">• 单单一个“中”字，就宣告了文化的源头活水。</span></strong></p></section></section></section></section><p><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 48px 25px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: center;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 48px 25px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: Arial; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(192, 0, 0);">讲师介绍</span><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(90, 90, 90); font-size: 14px;"></span></p><p style="margin: 0px 48px 25px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(123, 12, 0);"><strong><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/app6ovCb8Zj3569/image/ueditor/44908300_1555594795.jpg" title=".jpg" alt="640.webp (1).jpg" width="100%" height="auto"/></strong></span></p><p style="margin: 0px 48px 25px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(123, 12, 0);"><strong>王镇华老师</strong></span><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="color: rgb(90, 90, 90); font-size: 15px;">台湾德简书院主持人。师从一代大儒爱新觉罗·毓鋆。曾在台湾中原大学任教，乃古建筑专家。为了给年幼的女儿一个承诺：“小元，我答应你一个清新可喜的社会。”放弃教授之职，以喝稀粥的精神，回到家里创办书院，一晃二十八载。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="color: rgb(90, 90, 90); font-size: 15px;">著作：《黄河性情长江行》《百年中国的反省》《两岸文化的关怀》《觉者之路》《生活里的智慧》《明珠在怀》《有主有体，活得感心》《道不远人，德在人心》《中国建筑备忘录》《跟小元谈中国建筑》（金书奖）《书院教育与建筑》（金鼎奖）《空间母语》（金鼎奖）等。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="color: rgb(90, 90, 90); font-size: 15px;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="color: rgb(90, 90, 90); font-size: 15px;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.75em;"><strong><span style="color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(192, 0, 0); font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.5;">适合人群</span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="color: rgb(90, 90, 90); font-size: 15px;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="color: rgb(90, 90, 90); font-size: 15px;">适合每一个愿意走上自我成长之路的朋友</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: left; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="color: rgb(90, 90, 90); font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-weight: bolder; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: Arial; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: center;">适合人群</span></span></p><p style="widows: 1; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; font-size: 17px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;"><font color="#ffffff" face="Arial"><span style="letter-spacing: 1.5px; background-color: rgb(192, 0, 0);"><b>课程大纲</b></span></font></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p><br/></p><section style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal;"><section><section style="padding: 10px; text-align: center; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(240, 240, 240);"><section style="display: inline-block;"><section style="overflow-y: scroll; height: 344px; display: inline-block; overflow-x: hidden;"><section style="padding: 3px 2px; border-color: rgb(252, 180, 43);"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; color: inherit;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; color: inherit;"><strong style="color: inherit; font-size: 16px;"><span style="color: rgb(123, 12, 0);"></span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 27.2px; widows: 1; text-align: justify;"><strong style="max-width: 100%;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(123, 12, 0);">第一集：《生命就是天命》</span></strong><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">人人都有自主心，这本是老天爷给人的一份特别的礼物，自主心起心动念，天命就撂一边。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">人类问题的根源是——天赋的自主心，不会用。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(123, 12, 0);"><strong style="max-width: 100%;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px;">解卦：</span></strong></span><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 14px;">小心自己的起心动念——《震卦》</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><strong style="max-width: 100%;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(123, 12, 0);">第二集：《用生命真的去做》</span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">震跟艮关系就是周而复始。第二卦讲艮卦，自主心的发用基本都是为了取乐自我，如果你陷在泥潭里面，当然要知止。那正面止于至善是什么，就是道，自然万物没有东西能够超过它。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">生命的开展，需要有阳刚、正直的勇气。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(123, 12, 0);"><strong style="max-width: 100%;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px;">解卦：</span></strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">该止则止，能行则行——《艮卦》</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">生命的成长是最大的喜悦——《兑卦》</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">当生命陷溺时，需要超拔、猛醒——《巽卦》</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(123, 12, 0); font-size: 15px;"><strong style="max-width: 100%;">第三集：《小心负向思考》</strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">这四卦，是谈人做的事物、人为物。人为物，最经典的，就是挖井。挖井必须通天彻地，才能够成功。所以井给我们的启发就是，通天彻地，懂得天地人。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(123, 12, 0);"><strong style="max-width: 100%;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px;">解卦：</span></strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">中道通在天地，成德用于天下——《井卦》</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">困难对大丈夫是磨练——《困卦》</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">假的就是假的，真的就是真的——《贲卦》</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">不要留坏习气——《噬嗑卦》</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px;"><strong style="max-width: 100%;"><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(123, 12, 0);">第四集：《要光明才行得通》</span></strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">前面八个卦讲人心和人为物。现实社会里的人，最主要的就是物质的需求。有没有一种文明来安排分配的问题？有了争执，怎么样通过法制来解决？所以是需、讼、明夷、晋四卦。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(123, 12, 0);"><strong style="max-width: 100%;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px;">解卦：</span></strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">生命是目的，不是工具——《需卦》</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">争来的荣誉，不足敬——《讼卦》</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">面对已受伤的文明，要找到内在活化的出路——《明夷卦》</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">成德即修己安人，人人可行之道——《晋卦》</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;"><strong style="max-width: 100%;"><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(123, 12, 0);">第五集：《真正的大气》</span></strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">社会发展到富裕的阶段，本来是应该可以比较快乐地过日子，但事实可能相反，丰、旅、节、涣这四卦就在处理富裕了以后的问题。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">我们在台湾，有很深刻的印象，自己的一点福分都被耗尽了。被耗尽了，就是因为狂妄，因为有了钱，大器就出来了，这个大陆要小心。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(123, 12, 0);"><strong style="max-width: 100%;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px;">解卦：</span></strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">大要中，不容易——《丰卦》</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">人生如旅，小心琐琐志穷——《旅卦》</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">刚柔中肯，守形式之苦不是导正之法——《节卦》</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">面对涣散，要用阳刚生命振奋之——《涣卦》</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(123, 12, 0); font-size: 15px;"><strong style="max-width: 100%;">第六集：《幸福或灾难，都是自己打造的》</strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">做得完的都是小事，生命的大事做不完，但它反而是通畅的。这里面正在考验人类到底是舍得，还是舍不得现实中的一点利益。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(123, 12, 0);"><strong style="max-width: 100%;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px;">解卦：</span></strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">生命大事做不完，做得完的都是小事——《既济卦》</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">敢面对主体成长，才是大人——《未济卦》</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">中明，一个够大的开始——《离卦》</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">天无绝人之路——《坎卦》</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(123, 12, 0); font-size: 15px;"><strong style="max-width: 100%;">第七集：《生命里面长出来的信仰》</strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">内有德，外有道，人一定活在中道里面。只是因为自己的心用着用着，习气出来了，成见出来了。你以为自己的良心不见了，其实你内在的良知一直等你确认它，凭它你才能够与道呼应，走上中道。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(123, 12, 0);"><strong style="max-width: 100%;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px;">解卦：</span></strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">关键在德，考验在道——《中孚卦》</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">如何看待生活中的过错——《小过卦》</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">悟以顿法，行以渐法——《渐卦》</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">男婚女嫁，天经地义——《归妹卦》</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(123, 12, 0); font-size: 15px;"><strong style="max-width: 100%;">第八集：《天地万物的情义》</strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">接着我们讲感动的感卦。它把下面的心拿掉，上面是咸，咸阳的咸，意思就是交感，全部交感，而且有感应的。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">中国人有信仰，是一种超越宗教信仰的信仰。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(123, 12, 0);"><strong style="max-width: 100%;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px;">解卦：</span></strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">感应道交，不离中行——《咸卦》</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">天地间，唯有咸感是恒定的——《恒卦》</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">错受益，满招损——《损卦》</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">见善则从，有过则改——《益卦》</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px;"><strong style="max-width: 100%;"><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(123, 12, 0);">第九集：《教育是天大的事》</span></strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">良心的系统，中孚信仰的系统是什么？是诞生以后的启蒙教育。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(123, 12, 0);"><strong style="max-width: 100%;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px;">解卦：</span></strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">教育启蒙，乃通天之事——《蒙卦》</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">立天命，改命运——《革卦》</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">人生艰难，动在险中，大通在正——《屯卦》</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">人生如立鼎，建立稳健之人格——《鼎卦》</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(123, 12, 0); font-size: 15px;"><strong style="max-width: 100%;">第十集：《正家而天下定矣》</strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">一群人，生活在一个家里面，一个屋檐下，心还会违背，不同心协力，那这种心结叫做蹇，心很艰难的感觉。怎么解开？</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(123, 12, 0);"><strong style="max-width: 100%;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px;">解卦：</span></strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">乱世见大人，中节则大和——《蹇卦》</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">避免陷入“心疑、猜测和幻想”——《睽卦》</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">家道正了，天下也定了——《家人卦》</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">答案就在你心头——《解卦》</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px;"><strong style="max-width: 100%;"><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(123, 12, 0);">第十一集：《万物自养，人心养德》</span></strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">德行，是一步一脚印，渐修可以走通的路，德行的累积，可以把生命走通。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">君子有面对蛊惑的能力，并振起民心，培育正德。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(123, 12, 0);"><strong style="max-width: 100%;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px;">解卦：</span></strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">恃才傲物，恃德傲物，皆大过也——《大过卦》</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">养德积厚，而不是拾人牙慧——《颐卦》</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">内在的事，心悦诚服也——《随卦》</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">不事王侯，高尚其事——《蛊卦》</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px;"><strong style="max-width: 100%;"><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(123, 12, 0);">第十二集：《感谢中国还有实践的人》</span></strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">履、小畜、豫、谦讲德行的实践。其实清末明初的中国，就是实践力的萎缩。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">过度的内圣、过度外王的霸气，都还不是实践。就像人失了恋，拼了命上班，那个不是实践，那个反而是逃避中道。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(123, 12, 0);"><strong style="max-width: 100%;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px;">解卦：</span></strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">直面上天，自道自然——《履卦》</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">小步累积，德成大通——《小蓄卦》</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">法天地，顺而动——《豫卦》</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">谦虚并非自卑，好胜大多逞强——《谦卦》</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px;"><strong style="max-width: 100%;"><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(123, 12, 0);">第十三集：《回归道之大始》</span></strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">我们谈过“复自道”，这个大概是人类内在最大的呼唤，就是回到切身自己生命的成长，而不是任何短路性的东西，不是思想、不是概念、不是力量，都不是。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(123, 12, 0);"><strong style="max-width: 100%;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px;">解卦：</span></strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">人类一体，同人同心——《同人卦》</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">止恶扬善，才能大通光明——《大有卦》</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">如何看清当前的认同危机？——《比卦》</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">王者领众，以中道正心——《师卦》</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px;"><strong style="max-width: 100%;"><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(123, 12, 0);">第十四集 《阳刚的生命才有光辉的开展》</span></strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">尽管人方面的问题解决了，你还是会碰到无妄之灾，读到这一卦就觉得很妙！</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(123, 12, 0);"><strong style="max-width: 100%;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px;">解卦：</span></strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">无妄之灾，是诚信的二度考验——《无妄卦》</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">大止之教乃大养——《大蓄卦》</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">荟萃凝聚，贵在中诚——《萃卦》</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">登高自卑，行远自迩——《升卦》</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px;"><strong style="max-width: 100%;"><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(123, 12, 0);">第十五集：《十二阴阳消息卦（上）》</span></strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">十二阴阳消息卦，在农业社会，很容易发现大自然大生命的规律。因为春夏秋冬二十四个节气，跟农耕密切相关，但是到了《易经》，它不只是指农耕，还要指人性，尤其现实方面，要把自然法则包括人心的法则。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(123, 12, 0);"><strong style="max-width: 100%;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px;">解卦：</span></strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">以天为榜样，自强不息——《乾卦》</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">在阴的趋势中，要刹得住车——《姤卦》</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">退一步，海阔天空——《遁卦》</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">人生否泰，全系心神——《否卦》</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">守住天命，看着生命——《观卦》</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">不怨天，不尤人，阳刚三事——《剥卦》</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">整体、长远，才看得到正的好处——《坤卦》</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">人生的出路，不在远处，就在切身——《复卦》</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">不配天，志不立——《临卦》</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">心平何尝持戒，行直何用参禅？——《泰卦》</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">君子不用力量，用中道——《大壮卦》</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">除恶务尽，但非赶尽杀绝——《夬卦》</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(123, 12, 0); font-size: 15px;"><strong style="max-width: 100%;">第十六集：《十二阴阳消息卦（下）》</strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">宇宙万物都是靠阴阳，一阴一阳是为道，产生万物，但我们永远要记得阴余阳余,我们不自杀，我们不悲观，我们也不是乐极生悲，我们不搞那一套极端的。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(123, 12, 0);"><strong style="max-width: 100%;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px;">解卦：</span></strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">人生否泰，全系心神——《否卦》</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">心平何尝持戒，行直何用参禅？——《泰卦》</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">以天为榜样，自强不息——《乾卦》</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">整体、长远，才看得到正的好处——《坤卦》</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both;"><br/></p></section></section></section><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 14px; color: rgb(214, 168, 65);">上下滚动查看更多</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both;"><br/></p></section></section></section><p><br/></p><section style="font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; line-height: 27.2px; widows: 1;"><section style="max-width: 100%; font-family: Arial; border-width: 0px; border-style: none; border-color: initial;"><p style="color: rgb(49, 147, 105); font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; text-align: center;"><strong><span style="color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(192, 0, 0);"><br/></span></strong></p><p style="color: rgb(49, 147, 105); font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; text-align: center;"><strong><span style="color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(192, 0, 0);">内容精选</span></strong></p><p style="color: rgb(49, 147, 105); font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em;"><strong><span style="color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(192, 0, 0);"><br/></span></strong></p><p style="color: rgb(49, 147, 105); font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em;"><strong><span style="color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(192, 0, 0);"><br/></span></strong></p></section></section><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 27.2px; widows: 1;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/app6ovCb8Zj3569/image/ueditor/57663900_1555594795.cn/mmbiz_jpg/4ua5xvaf6lhxsawwsjdtmvk7pjtue3zwd8yjo3e7iauinbgic4j58amk8hhwvdhlh08siy6icnrdrjdz2y02bawsa/640" style="width: 677px !important; visibility: visible !important;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 12px;">中的演变</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 15px;">“中”在甲骨文，一个石头上面插着一个旗杆，一个飘带有一条两条三条的，风一吹，左右前后飘动，就表示生命现象变化万千，里面有个东西不动，就是你的天心、良知。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: center; line-height: 2em;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(123, 12, 0);"><strong style="max-width: 100%;">震卦</strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: center; line-height: 2em;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">小心自己的起心动念</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 27.2px; widows: 1;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; line-height: 27.2px; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: center;"><strong style="max-width: 100%;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/app6ovCb8Zj3569/image/ueditor/66858200_1555594795.cn/mmbiz_jpg/4ua5xvaf6lem6ic6lvrqowuvuhzsinceehndbmkruhyownibywetjwyr8xbleaqe2awpjt7fd5ibme9cmlw8ian49w/640" style="width: 364px !important; visibility: visible !important;"/></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 27.2px; widows: 1;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">人人都有自主心，这本是老天爷给人的一份特别的礼物。但要很小心，起心动念如地震，因为它的影响太危险、太厉害了。失之毫厘，差以千里。因此，圣人说：“君子以恐惧修省。”</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; line-height: 27.2px; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: center;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 18px;"><strong style="max-width: 100%;"><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(123, 12, 0);">艮卦</span></strong></span></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; line-height: 27.2px; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: center;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">该止则止，能行则行</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 27.2px; widows: 1;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; line-height: 27.2px; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: center;"><strong style="max-width: 100%;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/app6ovCb8Zj3569/image/ueditor/77470300_1555594795.cn/mmbiz_jpg/4ua5xvaf6lem6ic6lvrqowuvuhzsinceevn0kgamqqiok7ibjsyfcibxtmb7hn81rhdvpxypijnyxlxxl83tweeqa/640" style="width: 363px !important; visibility: visible !important;"/></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 27.2px; widows: 1;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">震卦主“动”，艮卦主“止”。在滚滚红尘中，要从正负两方面来体会何为“止”。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 27.2px; widows: 1;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">从消极的方面来说，有了过错，知道止之；从积极的方面来说，切身躬行，用生命真的去做，止于至善。这就是行中道，也就是行王道。故《中庸》里面会说：“故大德者必受命。”</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; text-align: center; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em;"><strong style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(123, 12, 0); font-size: 18px;">兑卦</strong></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: center; line-height: 2em;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">生命的成长是最大的喜悦</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 27.2px; widows: 1;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; line-height: 27.2px; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: center;"><strong style="max-width: 100%;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/app6ovCb8Zj3569/image/ueditor/89503500_1555594795.cn/mmbiz_jpg/4ua5xvaf6lem6ic6lvrqowuvuhzsinceegnyljmlxcsrqvpib935ok6ppnfqnx7n6vyjktqgcmzhviapcz75esbyq/640" style="width: 362px !important; visibility: visible !important;"/></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 27.2px; widows: 1;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">用喜悦，要正用才利。刚中悦外，这是顺乎天应乎人的做法。以喜悦带动群众，群众会忘其劳苦，甚至不在乎生死。因此，通透才有真正的喜悦。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">故云：“君子以朋友讲习。” 孔子乐于学，所以才会说：“学而时习之，不亦悦乎？有朋自远方来，不亦乐乎？”</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHe