, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; line-height: 27.2px; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: center;"><strong style="max-width: 100%;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/app6ovCb8Zj3569/image/ueditor/96563900_1555594795.cn/mmbiz_jpg/4ua5xvaf6lem6ic6lvrqowuvuhzsinceefazriaqedfwbz6xf27kibkkvmfcyhzniu1mpacogbhktc54chbvwk3bg/640" style="width: 368px !important; visibility: visible !important;"/></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 27.2px; widows: 1;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 15px;">天的运行，纯阳不息；君子的生命潜力，以天为榜样，自觉自行，自强不息。毓老师说：“天行健：天不感冒；自强不息：爸爸也帮不上忙。”既事言理，幽默到位。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 27.2px; widows: 1;"><br/></p><p style