26.file.myqcloud.com/app6ovCb8Zj3569/image/ueditor/5817200_1555594796.cn/mmbiz_jpg/4ua5xvaf6lem6ic6lvrqowuvuhzsinceep51mrtvt19tidnplo3x9hucklc1gdvbuzzevshjckybdjkzcisz4icq/640" style="width: 366px !important; visibility: visible !important;"/></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 27.2px; widows: 1;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">坤性顺，坤的贞是像母马柔顺个性，慢慢累积出来的正。这种成德者，积极努力，顺着客观本性一事一物的学，所以“先迷后得主”，即学得充实了，自己的精神（主）还是会出来。这时才见利。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; text-align: center; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&qu